Definition: a poisonous crystalline alkaloid extracted from the nightshade family
Example: used as an antispasmodic and to dilate the eye pupil; also administered in large amounts as an antidote for organophosphate nerve agents or organophosphate insecticides
Synonyms: noun, substance, alkaloid, antispasmodic, poison, mydriatic, antidote, a, poisonous, crystalline, extracted, from, the, nightshade, family, used, as, an, and, to, dilate, eye, pupil, also, administered, in, large, amounts, for, organophosphate, nerve, agents, or, insecticides
Category: noun.artifact
